726938f-a.title: Queens: Jackson Avenue - Thomson Avenue
726938f-a.text:
Jackson Avenue, east side, at Thompson Avenue, showing the Cueens
County Court House. Directly behind the Court House is the county
jail, seen in part.
March 23, 1932
P.L. Sperr
NO REPPODUCTIONS

726937f-a.title: Queens: Jackson Avenue - Thomson Avenue
726937f-a.text:
Jackson Avenue, south side, at Thomson Avenue. Shown is
part of the west side of the Queens County Court House and the
County Jail (right), seen from Court Square. The Works Progress
Administration is makihg improvements here.
Federal Art Project -- W.P.A.  November, 1936
Photographic Division
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE
